data.description: Welcome to this striking single-story home in beautiful Ave Maria, FL! With 4 BEDROOMS + DEN/3 FULL BATHS and a 3-CAR GARAGE on 2,500sqft, it offers impeccable design and functionality, making it the perfect place to call home. You will be greeted by a spacious and open floor plan, a light and bright color palette, 12' CEILINGS, and gorgeous plank tile. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring top-of-the-line SS appliances, ample cabinet space, walk-in pantry, large center island, quartz countertops, backsplash & breakfast bar.  Extended walk-in shower in the master bath. 3 additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for family and guests. The den w/French glass doors can be used as an office, a media room, a gym, a dining room, or even a 5th bedroom. Complemented by a FINISHED LAUNDRY W/CABINETS & UTILITY SINK. The large SCREENED-IN LANAI and landscaped backyard w/plenty of space for a pool on this OVERSIZED LOT are perfect for outdoor fun and relaxation. CENTRALLY LOCATED across from Donahue Academy, 2 blocks from the town center, & short distance of the 2-mile loop around the largest lake in Ave Maria. Amenities: Waterpark, walking trails, playground, golf courses &more!
